ry-lockfile-parser@1.9.1 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-resolve-deps@4.10.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-docker-plugin@9.10.0 › snyk-resolve-deps@4.10.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-resolve-deps@4.10.0 › snyk-module@3.2.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-docker-plugin@9.10.0 › snyk-resolve-deps@4.10.0 › snyk-module@3.2.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-nodejs-plugin@2.0.1 › snyk-resolve-deps@4.8.0 › snyk-module@3.2.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-resolve-deps@4.10.0 › snyk-resolve@1.1.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-docker-plugin@9.10.0 › snyk-resolve-deps@4.10.0 › snyk-resolve@1.1.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-nodejs-plugin@2.0.1 › snyk-resolve-deps@4.8.0 › snyk-resolve@1.1.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-policy@4.1.6 › snyk-resolve@1.1.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-go-plugin@2.1.2 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-module@3.1.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-mvn-plugin@4.7.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-nodejs-plugin@2.0.1 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-nodejs-plugin@2.0.1 › snyk-resolve-deps@4.8.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-nodejs-plugin@2.0.1 › snyk-resolve-deps@4.8.0 › snyk-try-require@2.0.2 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-policy@4.1.6 › snyk-try-require@2.0.2 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-nuget-plugin@4.2.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-policy@4.1.6 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-policy@4.1.6 › snyk-module@3.3.0 › debug@4.3.4\n* _Introduced through_: snyk@1.0.0-monorepo › snyk-sbt-plugin@3.1.1 › debug@4.3.4\n# Overview\n[debug](https://github.com/visionmedia/debug) is a small debugging utility.\n\nAffected versions of this package are vulnerable to Alternate solution to CWE-1333 | Inefficient Regular Expression Complexity. None\n# Remediation\nThere is no fixed version for `debug`.\n\n# References\n- [GitHub Issue](https://github.com/debug-js/debug/issues/957)\n"
